'''卡纳维拉尔角空军基地40号航天发射复合体'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://planet4589.org/space/jsr/back/news.350|title=Issue 350|last=McDowell|first=Jonathan|date=1998-02-22|work=Jonathan's Space Report|publisher=Jonathan's Space Page|accessdate=2009-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100503232748/http://planet4589.org/space/jsr/back/news.350|archive-date=2010-05-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.au.af.mil/au/awc/awcgate/au-18/au180051.htm |title=Table 3 |access-date=2009-08-22 |archive-date=2017-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830011131/http://www.au.af.mil/au/awc/awcgate/au-18/au180051.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> ('''SLC-40''')，即从前的'''40号发射复合体''' ('''LC-40''')是美国建于[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[梅里特島_(佛羅里達州)|梅里特岛]]的一个发射场。在1965年至2005年间，美国空军使用该发射台进行了55次大力神3号和4号火箭的发射。<ref name=afmuseum>{{cite web |url=http://www.afspacemuseum.org/ccafs/CX40/ |title=Launch Complex 40 |publisher=Afspacemuseum.org |date= |accessdate=2014-08-16 |archive-date=2014-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812210154/http://www.afspacemuseum.org/ccafs/CX40/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2007年4月25日，美国空军将发射场租给[[太空X|SpaceX]]用以发射[[獵鷹9號運載火箭|猎鹰9号]]火箭。<ref>Kelly, John: [http://www.floridatoday.com/floridatoday/blogs/spaceteam/2007/04/spacex-cleared-for-cape-launches.html "SpaceX cleared for Cape launches"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.floridatoday.com/floridatoday/blogs/spaceteam/2007/04/spacex-cleared-for-cape-launches.html |date=20070930030616 }}, ''Florida Today'', 25 April 2007</ref> 截至2022年1月，已经有[[獵鷹9號運載火箭發射任務列表|80枚猎鹰9号火箭]]从该发射复合体发射升空。<ref name="SpaceX">{{cite web|title=Launch Manifest|url=http://www.spacex.com/missions#completed-missions-header|publisher=SpaceX|access-date=2014-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406123343/https://www.spacex.com/missions#completed-missions-header|archive-date=2020-04-06|url-status=dead}}</ref>该地点在2016年9月的Amos-6事件后严重受损<ref name="NasaSpaceFlight">{{cite web|title=Falcon Heavy build up begins; SLC-40 pad rebuild progressing well|url=https://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2017/04/falcon-heavy-build-up-slc-40-pad-rebuild-progressing/|publisher=NasaSpaceFlight|accessdate=2017-04-22|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517125302/https://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2017/04/falcon-heavy-build-up-slc-40-pad-rebuild-progressing/|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，由于静态点火测试期间发生灾难性故障而导致<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spacex.com/news/2016/09/01/anomaly-updates|title=January 2 Anomaly Updates|publisher=SpaceX|accessdate=2017-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216160231/http://www.spacex.com/news/2016/09/01/anomaly-updates|archive-date=2017-02-16|url-status=dead}}</ref>。该综合体在2017年12月被修复并完成了CRS-13飞船发射任务。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/12/15/16759416/spacex-nasa-used-falcon-9-rocket-launch-live-stream|title=SpaceX launches and lands its first used rocket for NASA|publisher=The Verge|accessdate=2017-12-15|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208010926/https://www.theverge.com/2017/12/15/16759416/spacex-nasa-used-falcon-9-rocket-launch-live-stream|dead-url=no}}</ref>

